caption: Omg guys I can't believe you have noticed me!! Thank you so much. This one is about how you livin' . You deserve all of this because you have worked for it. I'm so proud of you. I'm going to keep posting shuttersongs because my dream is to go to U.S. But I can't afford it so please, if you could make my two dreams (the other one is to meet you)  to become true it would mean the world to me. I don't know if you will notice me again but I have to try. Now, as you guys have noticed me, I'm more motivated. Thank you?? If you motive me Again, can you guys follow me on twitter please (naashornah) thank you so much?? @jackjohnsonofficial @jackandjackofficial @jackgilinskyofficial #contest
